description:
Can you be sure you’ll receive the mark of God and not the mark of the beast that’s mentioned in Revelation 13:16? Many people are anxious to know what the mark of the beast is so they can avoid it, but few understand the real issues that are at stake. This episode looks at the nature of the final contest in the context of the three angels’ messages. How do you worship the beast? What is the image of the beast? What is the mark of the beast? Could a study of the word for “mark” shed some light on this subject? 

Discover what the Bible says about these things in this study with Walter Veith.

Watch more: https://adtv.watch/

Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialADTVChannel?sub_confirmation=1

Visit our website: https://new.amazingdiscoveries.org/
